<h2 id="Value-function"><a href="#Value-function" class="headerlink" title="Value function"></a>Value function</h2><ul>
<li>Value function: expected discounted sum of future rewards under a particular policy $ \pi$</li>
<li>Discount factor weights immediate <strong>vs</strong> future rewards</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>Used to quantify goodness/badness of states and actions</li>
